Greek Police Hold 10 in Soccer Match-Fixing Probe, Imerisia Says

-- B y   M a r c u s   B e n s a s s o n
-- 
2011-06-24T07:26:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-24/greek-police-hold-10-in-soccer-match-fixing-probe-imerisia-says.html
Police arrested 10 soccer officials
as part of an investigation into result-fixing in the Greek
soccer championship,  Imerisia  reported, without saying where it
got the information.  The officials appeared in court on Thursday following their
arrest the day before, the Athens-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marcus Bensasson in  Athens  at 
 mbensasson@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at 
 cstirling1@bloomberg.net . 